OL,6,FA knife killer who stabbed his victim
OL,7,Fnearly 50 times is to have his prison
OL,8,Fsentence increased by at least four
OL,9,Fyears, the Court of Appeal has ruled.
OL,11,FThe minimum 15-year jail term imposed
OL,12,Fon John Paul Whitla, 46, for murdering
OL,13,FNathan Gibson at an arranged meeting
OL,14,Fin Craigavon, Co Armagh was found to
OL,15,Fbe unduly lenient.
OL,17,FSenior judges established higher
OL,18,Fculpability based on premeditation and
OL,19,Fthe ferocity of the attack carried out
OL,20,Fin January 2020.
