OL,6,FShe also identified no mitigation
OL,7,Fapart from a reduction for Whita's
OL,8,Fguilty pleas.
OL,10,FAllowing the PPS appeal, the Lady
OL,11,FChief Justice quashed his original
OL,12,Fsentence and imposed a revised minimum
OL,13,Ftariff.
OL,15,F"The fair figure is 19 years, after
OL,16,Fwhich he becomes eligible for release
OL,17,Fon life licence if the Parole
OL,18,FCommissioners determine that
OL,19,Fimprisonment is no longer necessary
OL,20,Ffor the protection of the public from
OL,21,Fserious harm," she confirmed.
